# Vercel reads this file at clone time and applies it to ALL deploys
# from this repo, regardless of each project's Root Directory setting.
# So anything excluded here is gone for BOTH the web and the API
# projects.
#
# We don't aggressively exclude anything: the web project's `next build`
# needs apps/web + packages/ui + packages/types (workspace deps).
# The API project's Python bundler walks imports from api/index.py and
# only ships what FastAPI actually needs — apps/api + apps/ml — so it
# never bloats from having extra files visible in the build context.

# Local dev artefacts.
*.log
.DS_Store
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Build outputs (regenerated on every deploy).
.next/
apps/web/.next/
node_modules/
